    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document defines a YANG data model for fabric topology in data- center networks and represents one possible view of the data-center fabric.  This document focuses on the data model only and does not endorse any kind of network design that could be based on the abovementioned model.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
